        <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">We understand that some buyers value the convenience of dealer finance and are happy to pay a small premium for it. That is a valid choice. Our role is to ensure you are making that choice knowingly, with a clear understanding of the cost difference.</p>
